    "_comment": [
        "PASI (Psoriasis Area and Severity Index) 問診票",
        "開発: Fredriksson T, Pettersson U (1978)",
        "出典: Severe psoriasis--oral therapy with a new retinoid. Dermatologica. 1978;157(4):238-44",
        "PMID: 357213",
        "用途: 乾癬の重症度評価、臨床試験での標準指標",
        "医師による客観的評価ツール"
